INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('119', 'http://127.0.0.1:3001\\uploads\\2022051\\1651411317848.jpg', '2021初级前端面试题', '<h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">1.var let const 的区别</h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">var 会变量提升 let 和 const 不会<br/>var 在全局命名的变量会挂载到 window 上，let const 不会<br/>let 和 const 有块级作用域（暂时性死去），var 没有<br/>let const 不允许重复命名</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>2.Vue 里面 computed 是什么东西怎么用？</h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">在 vue 模板里面是有表达式是非常便利的，但是设计他们的初衷是用来简单运算的。在实际的开发过程中在模板里放入过多的表达式会让项目的可维护性大大降低。</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;div&gt;\n{{ data.split(\'\') ? data.split(\'\').reverse().join(\'\') : data.split(\'\')}}\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">对于这种复杂的计算单数据，我们应该使用计算属性来解决；<br/>计算属性中的方法是依赖于其中的值的，当计算属性中的值变化的时候，计算属性会更新</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">var vm = new Vue({\n  el: \'#example\',\n  data: {\n  data: \'Hello\'\n  },\n  computed: {\n    // 计算属性的getter\n    reversedMessage: function () {\n    // `this` 指向 vm 实例\n    return this.data.split(\'\').reverse().join(\'\')\n    }\n  }\n})\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">当 this.data 的值发生变化大时候，他所依赖的计算属性 reversedMessage 会重新计算并调用</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>3.Vue 里面的 watch 是什么东西怎么使用？</h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">虽然计算属性在大部分情况下都适用，但是在实际开发过程中需要一些自定义的监听器，当需要在执行异步或者开销比较大的操作中，监听器比计算属性更加有效。</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">watch：{\n  //需要监听的值\n  question（）{\n\n  }\n}\n</code></pre><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>4.watch和computed的区别</h4><blockquote style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">计算属性和监听属性都是希望在依赖数据变化的时候，被依赖的数据根据事先设定好的函数发生自动的变换。 watch 一个数据相应多个数据 computed 一个数据受到多个数据的影响 在实现原理上watch和computed是差不多的，vue 的data值在初始化阶段都会被挂载上 watcher 观察者模式，当数据改变的时候先调用watcher观察者模式，然后调用计算属性，和监听属性。本质上来说没有多大区别</p></blockquote><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>5.请说出 vue 几种常用的指令</h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-if：根据表达式的值的真假条件渲染元素。在切换时元素及它的数据绑定 / 组件被销毁并重建。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-show：根据表达式之真假值，切换元素的 display CSS 属性。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-for：循环指令，基于一个数组或者对象渲染一个列表，vue 2.0 以上必须需配合 key 值 使用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-bind：动态地绑定一个或多个特性，或一个组件 prop 到表达式。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-on：用于监听指定元素的 DOM 事件，比如点击事件。绑定事件监听器。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-model：实现表单输入和应用状态之间的双向绑定</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-pre：跳过这个元素和它的子元素的编译过程。可以用来显示原始</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mustache 标签。跳过大量没有指令的节点会加快编译。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-once：只渲染元素和组件一次。随后的重新渲染，元素/组件及其所有的子节点将被视为静态内容并跳过。这可以用于优化更新性能。</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>6.v-if 和 v-show 有什么区别</h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">共同点：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">v-if 和 v-show 都是动态显示 DOM 元素。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">区别：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">1、编译过程： v-if 是 真正 的 条件渲染，因为它会确保在切换过程中条件块 内的事件监听器和子组件适当地被销毁和重建。v-show 的元素始终会被渲染并 保留在 DOM 中。 v-show 只是简单地切换元素的 CSS 属性 display。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">2、编译条件： v-if 是惰性的：如果在初始渲染时条件为假，则什么也不做。直 到条件第一次变为真时，才会开始渲染条件块。v-show 不管初始条件是什么， 元素总是会被渲染，并且只是简单地基于 CSS 进行切换。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">3、性能消耗： v-if 有更高的切换消耗。v-show 有更高的初始渲染消耗。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">4、应用场景： v-if 适合运行时条件很少改变时使用。v-show 适合频繁切换。</p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>7.vue 中子组件调用父组件的方法</h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">通过 v-on 监听 和emit’触发 当前实例上的 自定义事件。 示例： 父组件：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;template&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"fatherPageWrap\"&gt;\n  &lt;h1&gt;这是父组件&lt;/h1&gt;\n&lt;!-- 引入子组件，v-on 监听自定义事件 --&gt;\n  &lt;emitChild v-on:emitMethods=\"fatherMethod\"&gt;&lt;/emitChild&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/template&gt;\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;\nimport emitChild from \'@/page/children/emitChild.vue\';\nexport default{\n  data () {\n  return {}\n  },\n  components : {\n  emitChild\n  },\n  methods : {\n    fatherMethod(params){\n      alert(JSON.stringify(params));\n    }\n  }\n}&lt;/script&gt;\n  \n&lt;!--子组件：--&gt;\n\n&lt;template&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"childPageWrap\"&gt;\n    &lt;h1&gt;这是子组件&lt;/h1&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/template&gt;\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;\nexport default{\n  data () {\n    return {}\n  },\n  mounted () {\n  //通过 emit 触发\n  this.$emit(\'emitMethods\',{\"name\" : 123});\n  }\n}&lt;/script&gt;\n结果：\n子组件 会调用 父组件的 fatherMethod 方法，该并且会 alert 传递过去的参\n数：{\"name\":123}\n\n</code></pre><h4 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>8.axios 有哪些特点？</h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">1、Axios 是一个基于 promise 的 HTTP 库，支持 promise 所有的 API</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">2、它可以拦截请求和响应</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">3、它可以转换请求数据和响应数据，并对响应回来的内容自动转换成 JSON 类 型的数据</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">4、安全性更高，客户端支持防御 XSRF</p>', '[\"前端\",\"vue\",\"es6\"]', '1652867826075', null, '31', '110', '1');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('120', 'http://127.0.0.1:3001\\uploads\\2022051\\1651411408906.jpg', 'router-view 组件间传值', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">情况1：router-view 子组件发生变化导致父组件发生改变<br/>父组件中：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;router-view @getMessage=\"showMsg\"&gt;&lt;/router-view&gt;\nshowMsg (val) {   // methods方法  val即为子组件传过来的值\n  console.log(val)\n}</code></pre>', '[\"vue-router\",\"vue\"]', '1651411408914', null, '31', '79', '0');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('121', 'http://127.0.0.1:3001\\uploads\\2022051\\1651411503795.jpg', 'es6-Promise解决回调地狱', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">1、什么是回调地狱?<br/>假如我们有很多异步事件，而这些异步事件又有很紧密的联系，比如一个异步事件要依赖另一个异步事件的返回值，看下面的：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"> $.ajax({\n        url: \'\',\n        data: {},\n        type: \'post\',\n        dataType: JSON,\n        success: function (res) {\n            $.ajax({\n                url: \'\',\n                data: res.data,\n                type: \'post\',\n                dataType: JSON,\n                success: function (res1) {\n                    $.ajax({\n                        url: \'\',\n                        data: res1.data,\n                        type: \'post\',\n                        dataType: JSON,\n                        success: function (res2) {\n                            $.ajax({\n                                url: \'\',\n                                data: res2.data,\n                                type: \'post\',\n                                dataType: JSON,\n                                success: function (res3) {\n                                    console.log(res3)\n                                }\n                            })\n                        }\n                    })\n                }\n            })\n        }\n    })\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">是不是进入了一环套一环的地狱里面。我们可以简单处理下：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"> function ajax1() {\n        $.ajax({\n            url: \'\',\n            data: {},\n            type: \'post\',\n            dataType: JSON,\n            success: function (res) {\n                ajax2(res.data)\n            }\n        })\n    }\n    function ajax2(data) {\n        $.ajax({\n            url: \'\',\n            data: data,\n            type: \'post\',\n            dataType: JSON,\n            success: function (res) {\n                ajax3(res.data)\n            }\n        })\n    }\n    function ajax3(data) {\n        $.ajax({\n            url: \'\',\n            data: data,\n            type: \'post\',\n            dataType: JSON,\n            success: function (res) {\n                console.log(res)\n            }\n        })\n    }\n    ajax1();\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">这样虽然把每个ajax请求放在了函数里面，不用把所有请求放在一个方法里面，但实际上还是在函数里面一层一层的嵌套来实现，很不便于阅读和维护。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">2、看看promise是如何解决的<br/>promise的出现就是为了解决异步编程中的回调问题，它提供了统一的 API</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">   const ajax1 = new Promise(function (resolve,reject) {\n        $.ajax({\n            url: \'\',\n            data: {},\n            type: \'post\',\n            dataType: JSON,\n            success: function (res) {\n                resolve(res.data)\n            }\n        })\n    })\n    function ajax2 (data) {\n        return new Promise(function (resolve,reject) {\n            $.ajax({\n                url: \'\',\n                data: data,\n                type: \'post\',\n                dataType: JSON,\n                success: function (res) {\n                    resolve(res.data)\n                }\n            })\n        })\n    }\n    function ajax3 (data) {\n        return new Promise(function (resolve,reject) {\n            $.ajax({\n                url: \'\',\n                data: data,\n                type: \'post\',\n                dataType: JSON,\n                success: function (res) {\n                    resolve(res.data)\n                }\n            })\n        })\n    }\n    ajax1.then(function (data) {\n        return ajax2(data)\n    }).then(function (data) {\n        return ajax3(data)\n    })\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">这就很很好的解决了回调地狱的问题</p>', '[\"es6\",\"promise\",\"js\"]', '1651411503800', null, '31', '92', '0');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('122', 'http://127.0.0.1:3001\\uploads\\2022051\\1651411584902.jpg', '一个人最好的生活状态', '<h2 style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 550; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 25px; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">一个人最好的生活状态，是该看书时看书，该玩时尽情玩，看见优秀的人欣赏，看到落魄的人也不轻视，有自己的小生活和小情趣，不用去想改变世界，努力去活出自己。没人爱时专注自己，有人爱时，有能力拥抱彼此。</span><br/></h2>', '[\"心情随笔\"]', '1651411584919', null, '31', '53', '0');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('126', 'http://127.0.0.1:3001\\uploads\\2022052\\1651424208256.jpg', 'vue之路由钩子函数', '<blockquote style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">vue路由钩子函数可以大致分为三类，他们的作用都是主要对路由的跳转进行控制，例如权限管理、登录判断、浏览器判断。</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">1.全局钩子<br/>主要包括beforeEach和afterEach,</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">一般有三个参数：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">to:router即将进入的路由对象</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">from:当前导航即将离开的路由</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">next:Function,进行管道中的一个钩子，如果执行完了，则导航的状态就是 confirmed （确认的）；否则为false，终止导航。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">通过beforeEach来对路由跳转做权限管理：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">// 设置路由\nrouter.beforeEach((to, from, next) =&gt; {\n  console.log(to, from)\n  // 跳转前判断是否需要登录\n  if (to.meta.auto) {\n    sessionStorage.setItem(\'success\', to.path)\n    if (store.getters[\'login/getLogin\']) {\n      next()\n    } else {\n      next({ path: \'pleaseLogin\' })\n    }\n  } else {\n    next()\n  }\n})\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">router.beforeEach 页面加载之前</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">router.afterEach 页面加载之后</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">2、单个路由里面的钩子<br/>beforeEnter和beforeLeave</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">beforeEnter: (to, from, next) =&gt; {          \n   console.log(to,from,next)\n},\nbeforeLeave: (to, from, next) =&gt; {\n   console.log(to,from,next)\n},\n</code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, Helvetica-Light, Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\">3、组件路由<br/>beforeRouteEnter和beforeRouteUpdate,beforeRouteLeave</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">\nbeforeRouteEnter(to, from, next) {\n   console.log(to)\n},\nbeforeRouteUpdate(to, from, next) {\n   console.log(to)\n},\nbeforeRouteLeave(to, from, next) {\n   console.log(to)\n}</code></pre>', '[\"vue\",\"vue-router\"]', '1651424208259', null, '31', '20', '0');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('134', 'http://127.0.0.1:3001\\uploads\\20220519\\1652962068988.jpg', '什么都没有深入理解 JavaScript 方法集的特性与最佳实践', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 236, 239); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2em; line-height: 1.25; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\">1 Array</h1><h2 style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 236, 239); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.25; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>1.1 array.concat(item…)</h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\">concat 方法会产生一个新数组，它是数组的浅复制，并把一个或多个 item 附加在其后。如果 item 是一个数组，那么它的每一个元素都会被添加：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; line-height: 1.45; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 3px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><div style=\"padding: 0.5em; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; overflow: visible; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> a = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'a\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'b\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'c\'</span>];\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> b = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'x\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'y\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'z\'</span>];\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> c = a.concat(b, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(86, 182, 194);\">true</span>);\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(c);<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//[ \"a\", \"b\", \"c\", \"x\", \"y\", \"z\", true ]</span>\n\n</code></div></pre><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; line-height: 1.45; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 3px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><div style=\"padding: 0.5em; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; overflow: visible; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//也可以用concat() 复制原数组并生成一个新数组</span>\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> a = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'a\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'b\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'c\'</span>];\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> c = a.concat();\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//此时c是a的副本</span>\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(c);<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//[\"a\",\"b\",\"c\"]</span>\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//c与a是不同的两个对象，他们在内存中分别被分配两块不同的空间进行存储，c仅仅是值与a相同，但是内存地址不同</span>\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(c == a )<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//false</span>\n</code></div></pre><h3 style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>1.2 array.join(separator)</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\">join 方法会把一个 array 构造成一个字符串。它先把 array 中的每一个元素都构造成一个字符串，然后再用 separator 分隔符把它们连接起来。默认的 separator 是逗号 ‘,’。如果想要实现无间隔连接，可以把 separator 设置为空字符串。</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; line-height: 1.45; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 3px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><div style=\"padding: 0.5em; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; overflow: visible; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> a = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'a\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'b\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'c\'</span>];\na.push(<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'d\'</span>);\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(a.join(<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'\'</span>));<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//abcd</span>\n</code></div></pre><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; line-height: 1.45; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 3px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><div style=\"padding: 0.5em; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; overflow: visible; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> a = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'a\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'b\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'c\'</span>];\na.push(<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'d\'</span>);\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(a.join());<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//a,b,c,d 默认为，号分割</span>\n</code></div></pre><h2 style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 236, 239); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.25; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>1.3 array.pop()</h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\">pop 与 push 方法可以使得数组像堆栈一样工作。pop 方法会移除 array 中的最后一个元素并返回这个元素。如果 array 是空数组，那么会返回 undefined：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; line-height: 1.45; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 3px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><div style=\"padding: 0.5em; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; overflow: visible; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> a = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'a\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'b\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'c\'</span>];\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(a.pop());<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//c</span>\n</code></div></pre><h2 style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 236, 239); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.25; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>1.4 array.push()</h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\">push 方法把一个或多个参数 item 附加到一个数组的尾部。它会修改 array。如果 item 是一个数组，它会把这个数组作为单个元素添加到数组中，并返回这个 array 的新长度值：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; line-height: 1.45; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 3px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><div style=\"padding: 0.5em; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; overflow: visible; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> a = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'a\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'b\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'c\'</span>];\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> b = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'x\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'y\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'z\'</span>];\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(a.push(b, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(86, 182, 194);\">true</span>));<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//5</span>\n<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(230, 192, 123);\">console</span>.log(a);<span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(92, 99, 112);\">//[ \"a\", \"b\", \"c\", Array[3], true ]</span>\n</code></div></pre><h2 style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 236, 239); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.25; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><a style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit;\"></a>1.5 array.reverse()</h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\">这个方法会反转 array 里元素的顺序，并且会修改数组本身，不会生成一个新的数组</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; line-height: 1.45; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 3px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46);\"><div style=\"padding: 0.5em; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"><code style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline; overflow: visible; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(198, 120, 221);\">var</span> a = [<span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152, 195, 121);\">\'a\'</span>, <span style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(152,